                        }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "id": "052be9a7da3342c88546c",
                    "stepText": "Now that you have the interference equation for the minimum thickness, rearrange the equation to solve for the film thickness $!$t$!$ in terms of the wavelength $!$\\lambda$!$ and the refractive index of oil $!$n_{oil}$!$. Which of the following expressions is correct?",
